OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople to be paid to use   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fless electricity on Monday 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Up to a million households in England, 
OL,6, Scotland and Wales will be paid to use 
OL,7, less electricity on Monday evening as  
OL,8, part of a scheme to avoid blackouts.   
OL,10,FNational Grid said its Demand          
OL,11,FFlexibility Service, which has only    
OL,12,Fbeen used in tests so far, would run   
OL,13,Fbetween 17:00 and 18:00 GMT.           
OL,15,FThose who have signed up will get      
OL,16,Fdiscounts on their bills if they do    
OL,17,Fthings like delay using their oven.    
OL,19,FThe cold snap has seen energy use rise 
OL,20,Fas more people turn on the heating.    
